{"tid":1133270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牛B死了！","createTime":"2019-05-01T02:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T02:20:20.000Z","uid":62646,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95783df54d8c19da9175e9c892432c33acc86a11","tid":1133270,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:16:19.000Z","msg":"西貢再發生撞死牛意外！晚上9時許，一輛新界的士沿西貢北潭路往黃石碼頭行駛，至北潭凹附近時撞到一隻牛B，之後絕塵而去，有途人見狀立即報警。警方到場調查，發現牛B已經傷重不治，而現場亦未發現涉事的士，僅在路面上發現一支懷疑的士留下的車燈，正嘗試聯絡司機了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者楊小姐向《蘋果》表示，當時現場有6隻成年牛及一隻牛B，突然有一輛綠的駛至撞向牛群，她形容的士車速甚快，撞到牛B後，司機竟未有停車及報案，「佢一撞完就即刻走，完全唔理隻牛B點，啲大牛圍住隻牛B，真係好慘」。她指牛B重傷倒地後，所有大牛都不願離開牛B身邊，不停以鼻輕擦牛B屍體，似是要將牠喚醒，情景淒涼，令人心酸。她斥責涉事的士司機冷血，完全漠視牛群的生命，「冇理由見到咁多牛都唔避，仲要橫衝直撞，我覺得個司機係專登」<br />\n<br />\n綠的撞死牛B司機不顧而去 目擊者：冷血 - <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190430&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59549752&amp;utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_medium=messenger&amp;utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190430%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59549752%26utm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_medium%3Dmessenger%26utm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEPjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=d82b594d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190430%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59549752%26utm_source%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_medium%3Dmessenger%26utm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=df6138fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190430&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59549752&amp;utm_source=whatsapp&amp;utm_medium=messenger&amp;utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link</a>"},{"pid":"a41848a8c036bc0f5f1cd88844d488029d84ec7d","tid":1133270,"uid":161159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1590a6b48bb6bde512012dbdd34